The Government has said construction of Magomeni residential apartments in Dar es Salaam will be completed January, 2021. Permanent Secretary(PS) for Works Sector at the Ministry of Works, Transport and Communications Arch Elias Mwakalinga has unveiled this during the visit at construction site. He said the project is being implemented by the Tanzania Building Agency(TBA) and financed by the government at the cost of 20/-bn. Arch Mwakalinga commended TBA for the good work asking the agency to complete the construction by December 2020.